snippet.title: Jay Shetty
snippet.description: I’m Jay Shetty - a storyteller, podcaster & former monk. My vision is to make wisdom go viral in an accessible, relevant & practical way. Check back for my videos that are posted each week on the topics of motivation, wisdom, love and relationships.
